{"tid":2246143,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一隻好玩既大陸原創game","createTime":"2020-10-16T20:38:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T15:44:19.000Z","uid":353380,"like":124,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"dece2e0daeee4739a6fdb09dbb13a04b73057670","tid":2246143,"uid":353380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:38:23.000Z","msg":"好似真係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那幾時先可以整一隻放得上枱既原創game<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到依家整既game都係左抄右抄, 咩原神, 王者, 第五人格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似日本既隻狼, 人中之龍都不停咁向外國輸出d日本文化<br />\n咁中國遊戲界做過d咩?<br />\n同中國最扯得上關係既game, <br />\n三國無雙, 莎木都係日本整既, <br />\n武俠方面, 細個玩既仙劍奇俠傳, 金庸群俠傳, 軒轅劍, 都係由台灣整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到依家支那遊戲界繼續做毒瘤抄game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似隔離個原神post咁講, 遊戲業界即將崩壞, 比呢個毒瘤整死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4323a1f7796f976c009cb59d1ba8dc65fb28f6fc","tid":2246143,"uid":323921,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:43:18.000Z","msg":"人地零幾年仲有咩專家學者推廣戒網癮，邊有可能鼓勵游戲開發呀"},{"pid":"0293f3081356fc92a83cbc729e3944a6e047ffa1","tid":2246143,"uid":116910,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T20:47:45.000Z","msg":"4399 個啲係大陸定外國既？"},{"pid":"4cf63257b5b662e7040eda1b5659807cf04fe32f","tid":2246143,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T21:05:55.000Z","msg":"同人遊戲好似有"},{"pid":"a6d253724748be28aa5b8f7f85f63af3b7a64b3f","tid":2246143,"uid":2419,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T21:14:54.000Z","msg":"大陸同原創係相反詞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72b07f552705a2c5bb0c0303e010e151b2c591d","tid":2246143,"uid":134559,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T2